Don't embed VCS info into EXTERNAL_JAVA_LIBRARY by default

This avoids contrib rebuilds under FORCE_VCS_INFO_UPDATE. This fixes of one of problems found here: lower than expected cacje hit on 2nd build.

EXTERNAL_JAVA_LIBRARY now doesn't have vcs info by default. Macro `EMBED_JAVA_VCS_INFO()` is introduced to explicitly add vcs info.

Explicit calls are added in places where vcs info is potentially useful (non-contribs and non-resources).
